<template>
  <v-app>
    <v-container>
      <!-- Top Bar -->
      <v-app-bar app color="blue darken-2" dark>
        <!-- Burger menu icon -->
        <v-btn icon @click="drawer = !drawer">
          <v-icon>mdi-menu</v-icon>
        </v-btn>
        <!-- Title -->
        <v-toolbar-title>{{ userName }}</v-toolbar-title>
        <v-spacer></v-spacer>
        <!-- Logout button -->
        <v-btn icon @click="logout">
          <v-icon>mdi-logout</v-icon>
        </v-btn>
      </v-app-bar>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <v-navigation-drawer app v-model="drawer" color="blue darken-2" dark>
        <v-list dense>
          <v-list-item
            v-for="(item, index) in sidebarItems"
            :key="index"
            @click="navigate(index)"
          >
            <v-list-item-action>
              <v-icon>{{ item.icon }}</v-icon>
            </v-list-item-action>
            <v-list-item-content>
              <v-list-item-title>{{ item.title }}</v-list-item-title>
            </v-list-item-content>
          </v-list-item>
        </v-list>
      </v-navigation-drawer>

      <v-main>
        <v-col cols="12" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto">
          <v-card class="mx-auto" max-width="600">
            <v-card-title class="blue darken-2 white--text"
              >Project Information</v-card-title
            >
            <v-card-text>
              <v-row>
                <v-col cols="12">
                  <v-text-field
                    v-model="project.name"
                    label="Project Name"
                    readonly
                  ></v-text-field>
                </v-col>
                <v-col cols="12">
                  <v-text-field
                    v-model="project.company"
                    label="Company"
                    readonly
                  ></v-text-field>
                </v-col>
              </v-row>
              <v-divider class="my-4"></v-divider>
              <v-row>
                <v-col cols="12" md="4">
                  <v-file-input
                    v-model="file1"
                    label="Upload File 1"
                    prepend-icon="mdi-upload"
                  ></v-file-input>
                </v-col>
                <v-col cols="12" md="4">
                  <v-file-input
                    v-model="file2"
                    label="Upload File 2"
                    prepend-icon="mdi-upload"
                  ></v-file-input>
                </v-col>
                <v-col cols="12" md="4">
                  <v-file-input
                    v-model="file3"
                    label="Upload File 3"
                    prepend-icon="mdi-upload"
                  ></v-file-input>
                </v-col>
              </v-row>
            </v-card-text>
            <v-card-actions>
              <v-btn color="blue darken-2" @click="submitFiles"
                >Submit Files</v-btn
              >
            </v-card-actions>
          </v-card>
        </v-col>
      </v-main>
    </v-container>
  </v-app>
</template>

<script>
import axios from "axios";

export default {
  data() {
    return {
      drawer: false,
      sidebarItems: [
        { title: "Proyecto", icon: "mdi-folder-outline" },
        { title: "Asesorias", icon: "mdi-account-plus-outline" },
      ],
      userName: localStorage.getItem("userName"), // Retrieve the user's name from localStorage
      project: {
        name: "",
        company: "",
      },
      file1: null,
      file2: null,
      file3: null,
    };
  },
  mounted() {
    this.fetchProject();
  },
  methods: {
    navigate(index) {
      switch (index) {
        case 0:
          this.$router.push("/student");
          break;
        case 1:
          this.$router.push("/student/asesorias");
          break;
        default:
          break;
      }
    },
    logout() {
      // Logic to logout the user
      // For example, you can clear any user data or tokens stored in localStorage
      localStorage.removeItem("token");

      // Redirect the user to the login page
      this.$router.push("/login");
    },
    fetchProject() {
      // Replace 'studentId' with the actual student ID or obtain it from the logged-in user context
      const studentId = "studentId"; // Example placeholder
      axios
        .get(`http://localhost:3000/projects/${studentId}`)
        .then((response) => {
          this.project = response.data;
        })
        .catch((error) => {
          console.error("Error fetching project data:", error);
        });
    },
    submitFiles() {
      // Handle file submission logic
      console.log("File 1:", this.file1);
      console.log("File 2:", this.file2);
      console.log("File 3:", this.file3);
      // You can implement file upload functionality here
    },
  },
};
</script>

<style scoped>
.v-btn i {
  color: white;
}
</style>
